gnu.crypto.tool
Class NessieHashTVEmitter

java.lang.Object
  gnu.crypto.tool.NessieHashTVEmitter
public class NessieHashTVEmitter
extends java.lang.Object

A utility class to generate NESSIE test vectors for a designated hash algorithm.

NOTE: The test3 test vector will be generated iff the global system environment variable named "TORTURE" is set. It is skipped otherwise.
